{"id":"1796","name":"happy-hour-whats-the-opposite-of-feel-good-friday","title":"Happy Hour: What&#x2019;s The Opposite Of Feel Good Friday?","author":"Christy Frink","date":"2009-05-01T18:17:00-05:00","tags":["adventure science center","bacon flu","contamination","grim","h1n1","harding academy","hiv","layoffs","medical equipment","metro budget","montgomery bell","pig flu","public forum","relay for life","revenue projection","st. vincent de paul","swine flu","tax increase","va hospital"],"categories":["News"],"contentEncoded":"<div id=\"greet_block\"><noscript><div class=\"greet_block wpgb_cornered\"><div class=\"greet_text\"><div class=\"greet_image\"><a href=\"http://nashvillest.com/feed/rss/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"http://nashvillest.com/wp-content/plugins/wp-greet-box/images/rss_icon.png\" alt=\"WP Greet Box icon\"></a></div>Hello there! If you&apos;re new to Nashvillest, you might want to <a href=\"http://feeds.feedburner.com/nashvillest\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>subscribe to our RSS feed</strong></a> to make sure you don&apos;t miss anything! We&apos;re also on <a href=\"https://twitter.com/#!/nashvillest\" target=\"blank\"><strong>Twitter</strong></a> if you&apos;d like to join us there!<div style=\"clear:both\"></div><div class=\"greet_block_powered_by\">Powered by <a href=\"http://omninoggin.com/projects/wordpress-plugins/wp-greet-box-wordpress-plugin/\" title=\"WP Greet Box WordPress Plugin\" style=\"text-decoration:none;\">WP Greet Box</a> <a href=\"http://omninoggin.com/\" title=\"WordPress Plugin\" style=\"text-decoration:none;\">WordPress Plugin</a></div><div style=\"clear:both\"></div></div></div></noscript></div><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://www.flickr.com/photos/paulnich/3479052998/in/pool-nashvillest\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.flickr.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\"><img class=\"aligncenter\" src=\"http://farm4.static.flickr.com/3651/3479052998_a20272ba74.jpg?v=0\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"375\"></a></p><ul><li>We were still trying to ignore swine flu headlines but it&#x2019;s not working. So we have paired this post with a picture of some cute meerkats at the Nashville Zoo to cheer ourselves up. [<a href=\"http://www.flickr.com/photos/paulnich/3479052998/in/pool-nashvillest\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.flickr.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">Flickr</a>]</li><li>The nasty swine flu may have spread to a second kid at Harding Academy. [<a href=\"http://www.newschannel5.com/global/story.asp?s=10289031\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.newschannel5.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">WTVF</a>]</li><li>Meanwhile, the Montgomery Bell kid with swine flu&#x2019;s mom wants us to know that we&#x2019;re not all going to die (maybe just some of us). [<a href=\"http://www.tennessean.com/article/20090501/NEWS01/90501065/-1/RSS05\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.tennessean.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">Tennessean</a>]</li><li>And while we&#x2019;re at it, St. Vincent de Paul School is closing for a week because lots of kids are feeling flu-y. [<a href=\"http://www.wkrn.com/global/story.asp?s=10288581\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.wkrn.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">WKRN</a>]</li><li>But if you hurry, through the rain, you can catch the Epic Swine Flu Forum at the Adventure Science Center tonight at 6:30pm. [<a href=\"http://www.newschannel5.com/global/story.asp?s=10288986\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.newschannel5.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">WTVF</a>]</li><li>Speaking of contagious diseases, a fifth person has tested positive for HIV after being exposed to some contaminated medical equipment at a VA hospital that may or may not be based here in Tennessee. [<a href=\"http://www.newschannel5.com/global/story.asp?s=10288900\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.newschannel5.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">WTVF</a>]</li><li>The Metro budget has been released and a lot of folks are getting laid off, but our taxes won&#x2019;t be going up. And hey, everyone at Metro who still has a job still gets to ride the bus for free. [<a href=\"http://www.wkrn.com/global/story.asp?s=10286439\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.wkrn.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">WKRN</a>]</li><li>And some economy experts have referred to our state&#x2019;s financial quandary as &#x201C;grim.&#x201D; [<a href=\"http://www.wsmv.com/money/19342954/detail.html\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.wsmv.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">WSMV</a>]</li><li>Adding insult to injury today, it&#x2019;s raining. Relay For Life is still on, but it&#x2019;s moving inside. [<a href=\"http://www.tennessean.com/article/20090501/NEWS01/904300357/-1/RSS05\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.tennessean.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">Tennessean</a>]</li></ul><p><em>Photo by <a href=\"http://www.flickr.com/photos/paulnich/3479052998/in/pool-nashvillest\" onclick=\"javascript:_gaq.push([&apos;_trackEvent&apos;,&apos;outbound-article&apos;,&apos;www.flickr.com&apos;]);\" target=\"_blank\">Paul Nicholson</a>.</em></p><p>Related posts:<ol><li><a href=\"http://nashvillest.com/2009/09/25/happy-hour-feel-good-friday/\" rel=\"bookmark\" title=\"Permanent Link: Happy Hour: Feel Good Friday\">Happy Hour: Feel Good Friday</a></li><li><a href=\"http://nashvillest.com/2009/06/01/happy-hour-its-all-about-gm/\" rel=\"bookmark\" title=\"Permanent Link: Happy Hour: It&#x2019;s All About GM\">Happy Hour: It&#x2019;s All About GM</a></li></ol></p>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<!--END .entry-content .article-->"}